Lady Tangwen Trahaearn is the leader of the Trahaearn Clan. During the Song of the Elves quest, the player finds her behind a crevice south of the Well of Voyage, and must repair her broken exoskeleton with a runite bar. After the quest, she can be found in south-east Prifddinas.

Transcripts Lady Tangwen Trahaearn speaks in:
  • The original colour of the Barrows Brothers armour
  • Transcript of Song of the Elves

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • This NPC is likely a reference to two Guildwars 2 NPCs: Tegwen, who Sylvari characters are introduced to in their personal story, and Trahearne, the leader of The Pact, who plays a major part in all character stories.
